comments: Sexton (CLE) and Simmons (PHI) engage and disengage off-ball.
Zizic (CLE) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Embiid (PHI) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Osman (CLE) makes hand-on-ball contact to slightly dislodge the ball from Simmons (PHI) during the rebound.
Osman (CLE) engages with Harris (PHI) as they both make natural moves towards the rebound.
Nwaba (CLE) makes contact to Simmons' (PHI) arm during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
Zizic (CLE) is firming up in legal position during the pick with Simmons (PHI) and does not deliver contact.
Harris (PHI) briefly brings an arm around Zizic (CLE), but quickly releases without affecting his FOM during the screen.
Zizic (CLE) is firming up in legal position during the pick with Harris (PHI) and does not deliver contact.
MOB shows Embiid (PHI) is not in a legal guarding position and he makes contact to Clarkson's (CLE) lower body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Simmons (PHI) cleanly dislodges the ball during the rebound with Sexton (CLE).
Clarkson (CLE) briefly engages with Embiid (PHI) in the high post.
Clarkson (CLE) makes some contact to Embiid's (PHI) body, but he is able to move through it during his shot attempt near the rim.
[Detectable with a stop watch] Clarkson (CLE) is in the lane for longer than three seconds.
LAR shows Embiid (PHI) makes contact to Clarkson's (CLE) body after the release that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
RLB shows Zizic (CLE) extends his arm into Scott (PHI) during the rebound affecting his ability to retrieve the ball.
Embiid (PHI) makes clean contact with the ball simultaneously as he makes marginal body contact during Zizic's (CLE) shot attempt.
Osman (CLE) commits a take foul on Embiid (PHI).
Clarkson (CLE) establishes and maintains legal position during the pick with Harris (PHI).
Simmons (PHI) beats Osman (CLE) to the spot and absorbs the contact as Osman extends his off-arm to dislodge him at the end of his drive.
Sexton (CLE) commits a take foul on Embiid (PHI).
Harris (PHI) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Clarkson (CLE).
